  <brief_title>Hyperfractionated RT With BCNU Versus Conventional RT With BCNU for Supratentorial Malignant Glioma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Comparison of Hyperfractionated Radiation Therapy (RT) With BCNU and Conventional RT With BCNU for Supratentorial Malignant Glioma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
