  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hyperfractionated radiation therapy (RT) to 72.0 Gy with BCNU will be compared to
      conventional radiation therapy to 60.0 Gy with BCNU to determine if hyperfractionated RT can
      improve the median survival time of adults with supratentorial malignant gliomas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
